A girl has died after being hit by a taxi on Nugget street and corner Plein street in Joubert Park in Johannesburg on Wednesday.It is reported that the girl was wearing school uniform at the time of the accident and was on her way to school.On arrival, Netcare911 paramedics found that the girl had already succumbed to her injuries. And was declared dead on scene.Occupants from the taxi sustained minor injuries, they were stabilised on the scene and transported to various hospitals in the area for further medical care.Police are on the scene investigating.-TNA Reporter 